code: @Bean @Order(0) public MeterFilter metricsHttpClientUriTagFilter(MetricsProperties properties) {     String metricName = properties.getWeb().getClient().getRequestsMetricName().     MeterFilter denyFilter = new OnlyOnceLoggingDenyMeterFilter(() -> String.format("Reached the maximum number of URI tags for '%s'. Are you using " + "'uriVariables'?", metricName)).     return MeterFilter.maximumAllowableTags(metricName, "uri", properties.getWeb().getClient().getMaxUriTags(), denyFilter). }
